      <accessrestrict id="aspace_ae5bdbabb08ef4d6929062e7e78bd210">
         <head>Conditions Governing Access</head>
         <p>The materials are open for research. Access to original audiovisual recordings is restricted. Consult the Beinecke Library Access Services department for information about reference copies.</p>  
      </accessrestrict>
      <processinfo id="aspace_a15030d729eb5dbd1d734823db9e1eb7">
